PrecisAmendments to the MIGRATORY BIRDS REGULATIONS to allow decoy hunting to increase protection for migratory game birds against excessive disturbances during the hunting season in Quebec and disallow baiting close to the opening of the hunting season, and permit use of raptors as a method of hunting migratory game birds (falconry) in P.E.I.
